Scanner UI Redesign — Wireframe-Matched Light Theme Demo
Commit: aaf097f40ee564d7fd461a9863069e34f1463b8b
Date: 2026-02-28
Branch: feature/ui-improvements

Files:
- index.html — Clean app shell, semantic HTML
- style.css — Wireframe-matched CSS (light theme, Inter font, CSS variables)
- app.js — Full scanner functionality with live API integration

Key features:
- Light theme (#f5f5f5 background, white cards) matching wireframe spec
- All scan modes: 0DTE, Weekly (This/Next/2-Week), LEAPs
- Smart Search with autocomplete
- Sector Scan with progressive disclosure
- Watchlist management via API
- Score circles (38px, color-coded), collapsible Trading Systems
- Dual-gate trade lock (Gate 1: score < 40)
- Responsive at 900px and 600px breakpoints
- Toast notifications, loading states
